<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-208-027 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 420 132</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  March 1 1991* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Inforum survey says buyers are frustrated.andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Blankenhorn, Dana.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Portman Cos. INFORUM Div. (Surveys).andO;Topic:     Computerworld (Periodical)Computer industryMagazinesSurveyUser NeedsTrade Shows.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>INFORUM SURVEY SAYS BUYERS ARE FRUSTRATED 03/01/91 ATLANTA, GEORGIA, U.S.A.,andO;1991 MAR 1 (NB) -- Technology buyers are frustrated by the cost ofimplementing new solutions, but it's up the manufacturers to find new ways ofdoing business.andP;  Those are the key results of a survey of technology buyersconducted by &quot;ComputerWorld&quot; magazine and Inforum, the Atlanta high-techtrade mart.andM;The report said trade shows are too cluttered and noisy, industrypublications don't provide the hands-on experience buyers want, and resellerscan no longer afford to do the support they once did because of shrinkingmargins.andP;  But there was some criticism of buyers too, saying they could&quot;develop methods of measuring the cost of buying in terms of staff effort,time, and travel&quot; and &quot;develop ways to let sellers know about their businessand the applications they need&quot; which &quot;don't require months of research forthe seller.&quot;andM;The key results of the study confirm the need for something like the Inforum,which leased prime space to the Atlanta Committee for the Olympic Games aweek ago.andP;  Inforum spokesman Kathy Kraft told Newsbytes the ACOG deal coversonly the top floor of potential showroom space in a market with 6 floors.andO;&quot;There's still plenty of space here,&quot; she said.andP;  &quot;Because ACOG is here, a lotof other companies may get involved now.&quot; And top executives worldwide willspend part of the next five years riding up and down Inforum's glasselevators.andM;(Dana Blankenhorn/19910301/Press Contact: Kathy Kraft, Inforum, 404-220-2700)</TEXT></DOC>